Charity -- Hi frequencies start softly, Add a "plinky" layer, which is repetitive. A mid-range tonal layer entrance. Scratching foreground texture adds, it's building nicely, then a sudden dropout for 5 or 6 seconds. From this point a fade-out. The piece should be normalized, since the file is at a very low volume. \
